{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778468158167,"sessionID":"ses_1eb12f387ffesheP3lf2SnOFwo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:43","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","content":"The requested obsoletions have been completed and are in PR #<NN>.\n\nSummary:\n- Obsoleted the four variant Entner-Doudoroff child terms with `replaced_by: GO:0061678`.\n- Obsoleted `GO:0061688 glycolytic process via Entner-Doudoroff Pathway` with `replaced_by: GO:0006096`.\n- Updated the parent `GO:0061678` with narrowMatch xrefs for the MetaCyc variants and removed the grouping xref.\n\nAll changes were validated via robot convert/reason and SPARQL QC checks before commit.\n\ncc: @raymond91125 @sjm41\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778468158162,"end":1778468158166}},"id":"prt_e14f66d1500110Ch9fc2Pn9ix2","sessionID":"ses_1eb12f387ffesheP3lf2SnOFwo","messageID":"msg_e14f65cdf001skUGY9RCor7bLm"}}
